e/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/session-store/design.md` -- Store interface (Redis/Valkey)\n- `/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/session-store/spec.md`\n- `/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/deployment/design.md`\n- `/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/deployment/spec.md`\n- `/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/deployment/client-go.md`\n- `/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/code-execution/design.md`\n- `/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/code-execution/spec.md`\n- `/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/cli-toolkit/design.md`\n- `/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/cli-toolkit/spec.md`\n- `/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/idle-cleanup/design.md`\n- `/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/idle-cleanup/spec.md`\n- `/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/integrations/design.md`\n- `/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/integrations/spec.md`\n- `/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/sandbox-orchestration/design.md`\n- `/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/sandbox-orchestration/spec.md`\n- `/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/python-sdk/design.md`\n- `/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/python-sdk/spec.md`\n- `/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/ci-cd/design.md`\n- `/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/ci-cd/spec.md`\n\n**No dedicated `specs/` or `docs/` directory exists.** Specs and design docs are co-located within each domain subdirectory.\n\n---\n\n### 3. pkg/workloadmanager Directory Status\n\n**The `pkg/workloadmanager` directory does NOT exist.** The current `pkg/` directory contains only:\n\n```\npkg/\n  apis/\n    runtime/\n      v1alpha1/\n        agent_type.go\n        agent_type_test.go\n        codeinterpreter_types.go\n        codeinterpreter_types_test.go\n        constants.go\n        constants_test.go\n        doc.go\n        groupversion_info.go\n        groupversion_info_test.go\n        shared_types.go\n        shared_types_test.go\n        zz_generated.deepcopy.go\n```\n\nThe AR-004 proposal explicitly targets creating `pkg/workloadmanager` as a new module.\n\n---\n\n### 4. HTTP Service Framework Patterns\n\n**No HTTP service code currently exists in the repository** (zero `.go` files with gin, http.Handler, router, or mux patterns). However, detailed HTTP service patterns are documented in design documents:\n\n**From `session-routing/design.md` (the Router component -- documented but not yet implemented in this repo):**\n\n- **HTTP Framework:** Gin (`github.com/gin-gonic/gin`)\n- **Server struct pattern:**\n  ```go\n  type Server struct {\n      config         *Config\n      engine         *gin.Engine\n      httpServer     *http.Server\n      sessionManager SessionManager\n      storeClient    store.Store\n      httpTransport  *http.Transport\n      jwtManager     *JWTManager\n  }\n  ```\n- **Route table pattern:**\n  | Method | Path | Middleware | Handler |\n  |--------|------|------------|---------|\n  | GET | `/health/live` | none | `handleHealthLive` |\n  | GET | `/health/ready` | none | `handleHealthReady` |\n  | GET/POST | `/v1/namespaces/:namespace/agent-runtimes/:name/invocations/*path` | Logger, Recovery, ConcurrencyLimit | `handleAgentInvoke` |\n  | GET/POST | `/v1/namespaces/:namespace/code-interpreters/:name/invocations/*path` | same | `handleCodeInterpreterInvoke` |\n\n- **Middleware pattern:** Concurrency limiting via buffered channel, `gin.Logger`, `gin.Recovery`\n- **Reverse proxy pattern:** `httputil.NewSingleHostReverseProxy` with custom Transport\n- **Health response shapes:** `{\"status\":\"alive\"}`, `{\"status\":\"ready\"}`, `{\"status\":\"not ready\",\"error\":\"...\"}`\n- **JWT auth:** RS256, RSA 2048-bit, 5-minute expiration\n\n**From `deployment/spec.md` (Workload Manager deployment expectations):**\n- Workload Manager deployed as a `Deployment` + `Service` named `workloadmanager`\n- Default HTTP port: **8080**\n- Health endpoint: **HTTP GET `/health`**\n- Router communicates with Workload Manager via `WORKLOAD_MANAGER_URL` env var (e.g., `http://workloadmanager.N.svc.cluster.local:8080`)\n- Session manager calls Workload Manager endpoints:\n  - AgentRuntime: `{WORKLOAD_MANAGER_URL}/v1/agent-runtime`\n  - CodeInterpreter: `{WORKLOAD_MANAGER_URL}/v1/code-interpreter`\n\n**From `test_spec.md` (expected Workload Manager API behavior):**\n- Sandbox creation endpoint: accepts `AgentRuntime` definition, returns `200 OK` with `sessionId`\n- Idempotency: same `name` returns same `sessionId`\n- Validation: missing `podTemplate` returns `400 Bad Request`\n\n---\n\n### 5. AR-004 and Related Architecture Decision Records\n\n**AR-004 is the current active change request:**\n- **Title:** \"WorkloadManager HTTP 服务框架\"\n- **Module:** `pkg/workloadmanager`\n- **Language:** Go\n- **Size:** M\n- **Status:** All sections are TODO placeholders -- proposal, design, delta-spec, and tasks are templates awaiting implementation.\n\n**Related ARs (dependency chain):**\n- **AR-001** (`changes/AR-001/`): CRD AgentRuntime type definition -- foundation for the API types\n- **AR-002** (`changes/AR-002/`): CRD CodeInterpreter type definition -- second CRD type\n- **AR-003** (`changes/AR-003/`): Shared types and constants extraction -- refactoring of AR-001/AR-002 shared types into `shared_types.go`, `constants.go`\n- **AR-004** (`changes/AR-004/`): WorkloadManager HTTP service framework -- builds on AR-001/AR-002/AR-003 types to provide RESTful API\n\n**Prompt file:** `/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/.sdd_prompt.md` contains the SDD (Spec-Driven Development) prompt for AR-004, including the full `deployment/client-go.md` spec as context.\n\n---\n\n### 6. Key Go Type Definitions (Existing Code)\n\n**API Group:** `runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh/v1alpha1`\n\n**Shared types** (`pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/shared_types.go`):\n- `ProtocolType` (enum: `HTTP`, `HTTPS`)\n- `AuthModeType` (enum: `picod`, `none`)\n- `TargetPort` struct (pathPrefix, name, port, protocol)\n\n**AgentRuntime CRD** (`pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/agent_type.go`):\n- `AgentRuntime`, `AgentRuntimeSpec`, `AgentRuntimeStatus`, `AgentRuntimeList`\n- `SandboxTemplate` (embeds `corev1.PodSpec`)\n\n**CodeInterpreter CRD** (`pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/codeinterpreter_types.go`):\n- `CodeInterpreter`, `CodeInterpreterSpec`, `CodeInterpreterStatus`, `CodeInterpreterList`\n- `CodeInterpreterSandboxTemplate` (flat fields: image, command, args, resources, etc.)\n\n**Current dependencies (go.mod):** `k8s.io/api v0.34.1`, `k8s.io/apimachinery v0.34.1`, `sigs.k8s.io/controller-runtime v0.22.2`, `github.com/stretchr/testify v1.11.1`. **Notably, Gin is NOT yet in go.mod.**\n\n---\n\n### Summary\n\n| Item | Status |\n|------|--------|\n| `proposal.md` files | 4 exist (AR-001 through AR-004), AR-004 is mostly TODO |\n| `pkg/workloadmanager` directory | **Does not exist** -- needs to be created |\n| HTTP service code in Go | **None exists** -- only documented in design specs |\n| HTTP framework pattern | Gin (documented in session-routing/design.md) |\n| AR-004 documents | proposal.md, design.md, delta-spec.md, tasks.md all exist but are templates |\n| `specs/` directory | Does not exist |\n| `docs/` directory | Does not exist |\n| Existing Go code | Only `pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/` with CRD type definitions (12 files) |\n| Workload Manager health endpoint | `/health` on port 8080 (per deployment/spec.md) |\n| Workload Manager API endpoints | `/v1/agent-runtime` and `/v1/code-interpreter` (per session-routing/design.md) |\n</task_result>","metadata":{"sessionId":"ses_2894d47bcffetgufRMLo4aXiiV","model":{"modelID":"qwen3.6-plus","providerID":"alibaba-cn"},"truncated":false},"title":"Explore agentcube project structure","time":{"start":1775812917312,"end":1775813059905}}}}
