{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775813071708,"sessionID":"ses_2894d6bf0ffeGcB7RdcCVqSSVz","part":{"id":"prt_d76b50f4e0019gTZa2FbpUi6JG","messageID":"msg_d76b4ff03001lrLlYH6vIGjcXp","sessionID":"ses_2894d6bf0ffeGcB7RdcCVqSSVz","type":"tool","tool":"read","callID":"call_260c8c6e475d49e6954c0ff6","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"filePath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/changes/AR-004/delta-spec.md"},"output":"<path>/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/changes/AR-004/delta-spec.md</path>\n<type>file</type>\n<content>\n1: # AR-004: WorkloadManager HTTP 服务框架 — Delta Spec\n2: \n3: ## Purpose\n4: \n5: <!-- TODO: 填写 Purpose -->\n6: \n7: ## Requirements\n8: \n9: <!-- TODO: 填写 Requirements (Gherkin 格式) -->\n\n(End of file - total 9 lines)\n</content>","metadata":{"preview":"# AR-004: WorkloadManager HTTP 服务框架 — Delta Spec\n\n## Purpose\n\n<!-- TODO: 填写 Purpose -->\n\n## Requirements\n\n<!-- TODO: 填写 Requirements (Gherkin 格式) -->","truncated":false,"loaded":[]},"title":"workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/changes/AR-004/delta-spec.md","time":{"start":1775813071701,"end":1775813071707}}}}
{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775813072986,"sessionID":"ses_2894d6bf0ffeGcB7RdcCVqSSVz","part":{"id":"prt_d76b513d0001ci5tFT1n2rHRUR","messageID":"msg_d76b4ff03001lrLlYH6vIGjcXp","sessionID":"ses_2894d6bf0ffeGcB7RdcCVqSSVz","type":"tool","tool":"read","callID":"call_505d976a95a9452b9aafeef7","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"filePath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/changes/AR-004/tasks.md"},"output":"<path>/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/changes/AR-004/tasks.md</path>\n<type>file</type>\n<content>\n1: # AR-004 任务清单\n2: \n3: > **Stage**: ST-1 (Proposal)\n4: > **Module**: `pkg/workloadmanager`\n5: > **Language**: Go\n6: > **Size**: M\n7: \n8: ---\n9: \n10: ## T-001: <!-- TODO: 任务标题 -->\n11: \n12: - [ ] T-001.01\n13: \n14: **验收**: <!-- TODO: 验收标准 -->\n15: \n16: ---\n17: \n18: ## T-002: <!-- TODO: 任务标题 -->\n19: \n20: - [ ] T-002.01\n21: \n22: **验收**: <!-- TODO: 验收标准 -->\n23: \n24: ---\n25: \n26: ## T-003: 全量验证门禁\n27: \n28: - [ ] T-003.01 `go build ./pkg/workloadmanager/...` 编译通过\n29: - [ ] T-003.02 `go test ./pkg/workloadmanager/... -v` 全部通过\n30: \n31: **验收**: 全部检查项通过，AR-004 可标记为完成\n\n(End of file - total 31 lines)\n</content>","metadata":{"preview":"# AR-004 任务清单\n\n> **Stage**: ST-1 (Proposal)\n> **Module**: `pkg/workloadmanager`\n> **Language**: Go\n> **Size**: M\n\n---\n\n## T-001: <!-- TODO: 任务标题 -->\n\n- [ ] T-001.01\n\n**验收**: <!-- TODO: 验收标准 -->\n\n---\n\n## T-002: <!-- TODO: 任务标题 -->\n\n- [ ] T-002.01","truncated":false,"loaded":[]},"title":"workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/changes/AR-004/tasks.md","time":{"start":1775813072978,"end":1775813072984}}}}
